                {
                    "class": "DepictionMarkdownView",
                    "markdown": "- Wide variety of font styles, including modern, classic, and minimalistic designs.\n- Full support for system-wide font changes.\n- Easy-to-use preference pane for customizing fonts per app.\n- Dynamic font rendering for clear and sharp text on all devices."
                },
                {
                    "class": "DepictionSubheaderView",
                    "useBoldText": true,
                    "useBottomMargin": false,
                    "title": "Preferences"
                },
                {
                    "class": "DepictionMarkdownView",
                    "markdown": "- **Enable**: Turn A-Font on or off.\n- **Font Style**: Choose from a variety of pre-installed fonts.\n- **Per-App Fonts**: Set different fonts for specific apps.\n- **Font Size**: Customize the size of the fonts globally or per app.\n- **Bold Text**: Enable or disable bold text for all fonts."
                },
                {
                    "class": "DepictionSubheaderView",
                    "useBoldText": true,
